---
title: Mild Indian Salmon Curry with Roasted Veggies & Basmati Rice
description: Delicately spiced and luxuriously creamy, this mild curry is sure to hit the spot! It’s packed full of flaky salmon and roasted veggies, making it ultra satiating - serve it over fluffy basmati rice and dig in!
